ActNational Capital Act
SubjectCity of Ottawa Five year renewal option 35 George Street
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant a five-year renewal option, starting January 1, 2013, to an existing five-year lease with the City of Ottawa, located at 35 George Street in Ottawa.
